
Not_Compatible
==Syntax==
Not_Compatible,OSType
==Parameters==
1OSTypeProject target type for which the current script is not compatibleLiveXPScript is not compatible with the LiveXP projectVistaPEScript is not compatible with the VistaPE projectWin7PEScript is not compatible with the Win7PE projectRemarks
Tihs function is used to generate an error message if the script is used in a none compatible project.
==Example==
This will generate an error message at build time if the script is built in the LiveXP project.
Not_Compatible,LiveXP
